@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_abzdyt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.44 + v0 + 0.69)) / 0.09)
    v1 = (wp.sin(v2) - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.51) - (v0 + 0.08 * v1 + 0.50)))
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = wp.sin(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
